Author: earlgrey-tea-
Text: I’m so proud of you for doing that for yourself!! That sounds really scary :P

Author: blueberrypancakespls
Text: hey I was in a position similar to you not too long ago. I was scared to tell my parents because I just didn’t really want to admit it to them (I ended up telling them first) but I made a back up plan which was to go talk to a mental health counselor at my school (ended up doing that too) because they will take you seriously and will help you find the support you need
